ultiverse之中.<br />\n<br />\nMetal第一期已經見到SS呢個故事運用大量Morrison既創作. <br />\n但係喺本身已經難明既Morrison故事上面再寫就更加複雜, 所以第一期都睇得幾苦下.<br />\n<br />\n不過呢本lost就完全唔同了.<br />\n今次SS將golden age, Morrison同佢自己N52既野結合得非常精彩. <br />\n成個故事重好有Morrison既味道.<br />\nCourt of owls之後SS最佳既Batman書就係呢本.<br />\n值得大家買返本睇."},{"pid":"a3468a64013e46ed41ef83dd99f4d50a8051d8f1","tid":463052,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cbr.com/batman-lost-major-2018-dc-event-clue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbr.com%2Fbatman-lost-major-2018-dc-event-clue%2F&d=e%2B11qaBe0KYJzSebqjOx1TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e7e8f0ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbr.com/batman-lost-major-2018-dc-event-clue/</a><br />\nSS話個書櫃隱藏左18年event既伏線<br />\nCBR詳細分析"},{"pid":"f93d11ccb66c651365a1e7fef121d47806ee420e","tid":463052,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"Batman Surrendered. The world is ending."},{"pid":"abd8c232fe7d5985d8d3796e3b2b64f6a0d1958b","tid":463052,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Batman Surrendered. The world is ending.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上期Metal最後都見到bruce好無力"},{"pid":"a585803d610be253079a54ab45888d37f3a1a2a2","tid":463052,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T11:34:39.000Z","msg":"Greg Capullo啲畫明顯地差左"},{"pid":"70f9e5408d9aebdbb48e506eca2b64692e0e1111","tid":463052,"uid":40217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Batman Surrendered. The world is ending.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上期Metal最後都見到bruce好無力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係真,Metal入面GE佢明顯有D不知所措"},{"pid":"8a00430fc3feac5f41abbdbc86a41f74c9d88f3b","tid":4630